{"tid":1126111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手機支付召妓易被捕？傳公安以大數據捉 1200 嫖客","createTime":"2019-04-26T06:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T07:17:49.000Z","uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a70cee1bf8924b73b8a2a2bc26bb45618bccbc1","tid":1126111,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2335000/2335570/3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2335000%2F2335570%2F3_1024.jpg&h=d02fe4f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時各種消費，很多時都可以使用電子支付，在中國大陸，甚至連召妓都可使掃二維碼找數。有內地媒報道，早前江蘇省宜興市警方翻查二維條碼轉帳記錄，之後一口氣傳召 1200 人調查，原因是他們在涉黃洗浴中心消費了 600 元以上人民幣，被「涉嫌嫖娼」強制傳喚，更指警方如此利用大數據抓嫖是「全國首例」。<br />\n<br />\n【科技】教學助理擅長電腦打印技術！竟於學校自製偽鈔用於嫖妓<br />\n<br />\n在網絡流傳的截圖顯示，有人收到宜興市公安局環科園派出所警察發出的短訊，內容是收訊者「涉嫌嫖娼」，需聯繫派出所「主動投案」，向公安機關如實供述自己的違法行為的，減輕或者不予處罰，否則將視為拒絕接受傳喚，公安機關將上門強制傳喚。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳開後，馬上惹來不少人質疑。有律師認為執法過火，不符合程序正義原則，把這些人傳喚去是有罪推定。按此邏輯，任何人都可能被羅織追訴，而且要來自證清白，每個人都可能被構陷於罪。有大陸網民則嘲諷這是當局「限價嫖娼」，留言表示「看來以後要改用現金了，又提醒「嫖客」趕快註銷微信（條碼支付）帳號，或是「下次分開付，每筆 300」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2335000/2335570/1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2335000%2F2335570%2F1_600.jpg&h=8f355852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n也許因為消息愈傳愈厲害，宜興警方回應，傳喚這些<br />\n<br />\n人到警所僅僅是接受調查、說明情況，至於是否真的嫖娼，警方會根據證據來認定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2335570/%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%8F%AC%E5%A6%93%E6%98%93%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%EF%BC%9F%E5%82%B3%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E6%8D%89%201200%20%E5%AB%96%E5%AE%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2335570%2F%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2594%25AF%25E4%25BB%2598%25E5%258F%25AC%25E5%25A6%2593%25E6%2598%2593%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25EF%25BC%259F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E6%258D%2589%25201200%2520%25E5%25AB%2596%25E5%25AE%25A2&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=c1a8f6d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2335570/%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%8F%AC%E5%A6%93%E6%98%93%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%EF%BC%9F%E5%82%B3%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E6%8D%89%201200%20%E5%AB%96%E5%AE%A2</a>"},{"pid":"9cf7b5eef5035d60dc0d48649863919b101fc4d4","tid":1126111,"uid":196484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:58:13.000Z","msg":"呢道係中國 唔需要證據 我對眼就係證據"},{"pid":"32df726503279cb36e1577354d03ab56dbe9662f","tid":1126111,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:10:06.000Z","msg":"咁撚蠢都有"},{"pid":"7c3c31a879774b962765237dad978777ec21c3fb","tid":1126111,"uid":92734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"雷鼎嗚教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb97b45f030c4d272d7bfcacb274083a79754f39","tid":1126111,"uid":14511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"洗錢洗左去邊都可以俾人追蹤翻，中國好棒棒"},{"pid":"c383a2930fd334fe61aaf7bed014f70bc841efee","tid":1126111,"uid":61648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"支付寶真係好方便 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人拉果方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />證據都幫人搵埋"}]}